title: Spotify Lawsuit Alleges Billions of Streams, Including Some of Drake’s, Are Fraudulent
description: A class action lawsuit alleges that Spotify has turned a blind eye to ‘streaming fraud,’ as bots increase streaming numbers and revenue for some artists.

title: Jaguar Land Rover Settlement Ends Class Action Lawsuit Over Allegedly Defective Turbochargers
description: A Jaguar Land Rover settlement offers compensation to current/former owners and lessees whose vehicles were equipped with allegedly defective turbochargers.

title: Naked Nutrition Lawsuit Alleges Mass Gainer Vegan Protein Powder Contains Dangerous Levels of Heavy Metals
description: A class action lawsuit alleges that Naked Nutrition vegan protein powder contains dangerous levels of lead.
